(2, 'About Us', 0, 'About Us', '1389790101_1389790101.jpg', NULL, NULL, 'about-us', 'pagetemplates/default_template', 0, NULL, '', '', '', '<p>Datanomers, a Big Data Analytics Company has successfully guided customers on how to leverage machine learning algorithms in data analytics for automation to improve productivity, drive more business and make better business decisions that will give them a competitive edge.<br />\r\nDatanomers has been offering Big Data Solutions through it&rsquo;s partner, IPsoft <a href="http://www.ipsoft.com" target="_blank"><u>www.ipsoft.com</u></a>. We have helped several fortune 100 customer like Verizon, Tata Communications, KDDI etc</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Deepak Dube, Ph.D.<br />\r\nFounder, President &amp; CEO</strong><br />\r\nDeepak Dube graduated from Illinois Institute of Technology in 1988 with an MS in Computer science. He received his doctorate in Computer Science in 1994 in performance modeling of mobile networks. He worked at Bell Labs for over 20 years as a research scientist in wireless networks, working on access technologies. He pioneered Quality of Service for converged networks; his patents and research led to the implementation of voice-video-data networks.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Early on, he saw the immense impact intelligent machines would have on society; to see this vision take shape, he founded Datanomers and launched statistical machine learning solutions which led the drive for &quot;automation through machine intelligence.&quot; Most recently, he has coupled machine learning with &ldquo;big data analytics&rdquo; to roll out advanced technology solutions for better business insights, strategy and execution.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Pranay Kumar Pogde<br />\r\nCo-Founder, President Engineering </strong><br />\r\nAs President of Engineering, Pranay is responsible for delivering on promise to customers and steering company&rsquo;s strategic technology innovation initiatives.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Prior to founding Datanomers Pranay served as a senior product architect at CTO office at Juniper Networks and played technical leadership roles in wired and wireless networking product business unit at Juniper. Pranay has led, built and delivered several engineering products over past 18 years at Juniper Networks, Caspian Networks, Nokia Inc, AT&amp;T and Hughes Systems.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Pranay received a bachelor&#39;s degree in computer science from National Institute of Technology Nagpur, India (VNIT, 1994) and master&#39;s degree in computer science and automation from Indian Institute of Science Bangalore, India (IISc, 1996). Pranay has several patents pending on scalable network architectures.</p>\r\n', NULL, NULL, 1, '2014-01-14 07:32:33', '2014-01-23 02:47:54'),
(3, 'Solutions', 0, 'Solutions', '1389858401_1389858401.jpg', NULL, NULL, 'solutions', 'pagetemplates/default_template', 1, NULL, '', '', '', '<p>We build Big Data analytics solutions that offer Actionable Intelligence. Accuracy is our hallmark and claim to fame. Our solutions are unique: they are expert systems that, based on advanced machine learning, are accurate, easy to operate, and automate processes. Your business is competitive - now more than ever, you need to differentiate from competitors, with better service to high value customers, delivered cost-effectively. You need to get ahead of competitors in your business processes to pursue opportunities objectively. That&rsquo;s what our solutions help you deliver. We guarantee you that. How? Because, our advanced analytics and machine-learning state-of-the-art technology offers business insight and intelligence, accurately &ndash; all at very reasonable price. this is a testtest</p>\r\n', NULL, NULL, 1, '2014-01-14 07:33:56', '2014-01-17 00:56:48'),
(4, 'Professional Services', 0, 'Professional Services', '1389878730_1389878730.jpg', NULL, NULL, 'professional-services', 'pagetemplates/default_template', 0, NULL, '', '', '', '<p>The technology services that run your business are complex. The complexity, unless tackled and managed seamlessly you invariably incur delays and downtime. Your company&rsquo;s data is growing exponentially. Without proper systems in place to manage, organize and glean intelligent insights from this growing data, you will not only drown in, but also lose your competitive edge.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>How do you tackle this complexity? What&rsquo;s the solution? You must bring in innovations that bring substantial value and lasting competitive advantage to your business. You must bring disruption to your existing monitoring and management strategy to perform adaptive and full-service automation. To combat the onslaught of this complexity, you can no longer just rely on human intelligence and workforce. You must employ intelligent machines to analyze variables of your business and to automate remediation measures.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You need Big Data analytics! It is the disruptive force that when applied right, helps you bring productive disruption to your management processes. Big Data promises to manage the complexity and helps make better informed decisions. But, are you ready for Big Data? How do put Big Data to practice &ndash; beyond hype?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Datanomers can help you address the questions and provide solutions. Our strategic consulting and professional services in big data include readiness assessment, foundational architecture and accurate analytics that help you extract the business intelligence from huge volume of data and myriads of data sources. Our patented Big Data statistical solutions are the next level in automation and provide deep insights to customers and enable effective business decision making.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Our Approach:</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Our approach is to understand your business through in-depth discussions, develop strategic requirements that align with your long term objectives, identify technology solutions to meet the requirements and provide roadmap to implement customized Big Data solutions at a reasonable cost. We develop and deliver programs designed around your specific business goals using a foundation of research and insights across technologies, geographies and industries as well as expertise across practice areas that span strategy, sales and marketing, and business measurement and management.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Datanomers custom solutions harness the power of advanced autonomics, thought leadership, and innovative best practices to drive your business forward. With proven approaches and research-backed methodologies, Datanomers helps you build successful business strategies and make informed decisions for planning, budgeting, sales and marketing strategies. So you can engage your customer&rsquo;s and best of all, measure all aspects of your business.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Big Data Professional Services Portfolio:</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Big Data Analytics</li>\r\n	<li>Real-Time Big Data &ndash; Expedited Reports Through Dashboard</li>\r\n	<li>Roadmap/Readiness Assessment from Big Data</li>\r\n	<li>Data Integration - ETL</li>\r\n	<li>Data Mining and Visualization</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>Big Data Professional Services:</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>We conduct extensive readiness assessment from. With your input, we short list, prioritize and define which business relevant outcomes we need to target, study and analyze. We help collect and sanitize data from variety of sources and in variety of formats. We help ingest and transform data (both structured and unstructured). We size the solution right for your data (volumes) and your speed (velocity) requirements. We propose the right blend of technologies based on your analytics needs - real-time or batch-analytics.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We assist you with capacity planning based on the analysis of your existing resources health and data growth trends. We assist you with making decisions on: which technologies to select (search, text-analytics, data mining etc.), what platform, and which vendors. We help you address cross-organization challenges for data management. In a nutshell, we hand hold you through the process of readiness assessment to ascertain &ndash; are you ready? If not, what would it take?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Unstructured data for analytics must be stored and accessed differently than core enterprise data. We will design your big data storage infrastructure using best practices with an in-depth understanding of the unique data, analytics and complex requirements. We can maximize your storage investments, reduce risks and assure that your cluster performs optimally and can easily scale as your data and workloads.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We help define a foundational architecture that must address volume, variety, velocity and most importantly veracity (accuracy) aspects of big data analytics. Veracity has to address - data sanitization, noise elimination, identify relationships with proven statistical techniques and measures {scatter plots, correlation, clustering, entropy, percentiles and more}. A well-defined and well-built foundational architecture goes long way to support multiple big-data projects.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We will work with customers and partners to evaluate the potential big data analytics can have on your business and systems before you invest. We will closely examine the use cases and goals to prove the prototype functionality and will document the process and results for use in production. A POC entails the architecture, design, deployment of technologies, data load and results testing. We then provide documentation of the process and findings a production pilot recommendations.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We help define cross-organizational processes around data ingestion, data management and actionable analytics. Post-readiness assessment review, we help seek approval, build teams and execute to the projects.</p>\r\n', NULL, NULL, 1, '2014-01-14 07:39:07', '2014-01-16 08:25:30'),
