(6, 'Resources', 0, 'Resources', '1389851376_1389851376.jpg', NULL, NULL, 'resources', 'parent_page', 0, NULL, '', '', '', '<div class="video first"><iframe allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" height="250" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/0nik7IucWRQ?rel=0" width="100%"></iframe></div>\r\n\r\n<div class="video"><iframe allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" height="250" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/AiD3lI3K5Yo?rel=0" width="100%"></iframe></div>\r\n\r\n<div class="video last"><iframe allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" height="250" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/OO_P7A18M_0?rel=0" width="100%"></iframe></div>\r\n\r\n<h3 class="heading-main" style="float:left; margin-top:30px;">Case study</h3>\r\n\r\n<div class="pdf">\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href="http://datanomers.checkyourprojects.com/app/webroot/ck_files/files/BigData.pdf" target="_blank">Click here</a> to see our BigData Solutions</li>\r\n	<li><a href="http://datanomers.checkyourprojects.com/app/webroot/ck_files/files/BigData_Solutions.pdf" target="_blank">Click here</a> to see our BigData</li>\r\n	<li><a href="http://datanomers.checkyourprojects.com/app/webroot/ck_files/files/ProductSheetFM-V2_2(1).pdf" target="_blank">Click here</a> to see our Product SheetFM-V2.2</li>\r\n	<li><a href="http://datanomers.checkyourprojects.com/app/webroot/ck_files/files/ProductSheetST.pdf" target="_blank">Click here</a> to see our Product SheetST</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n', NULL, NULL, 1, '2014-01-14 07:42:56', '2014-01-23 07:10:14'),
(7, 'Intelligent Analytical Modelerâ„¢', 3, 'Intelligent Analytical Modeler', '1389778684_1389778684.jpg', NULL, NULL, 'intelligent-analytical-modeler', 'Pages/pagetemplates/full_page', 0, NULL, '', '', '<p>There are challenges to discover what parameters to study that impact a business outcome. Relationships between myriads of parameters, characteristic of parameters - are difficult to define. Once the parameters are discovered, you&#39;re confronted with the next challenge: sanitize the data before processing it. Subject matter experts must statistically analyze relationships between parameters to weed out noise and outliers.</p>\r\n', '<div class="left-side"><img alt="" src="http://datanomers.checkyourprojects.com/app/webroot/ck_files/images/inteletical.png" /></div>\r\n\r\n<p>There are challenges to discover what parameters to study that impact a business outcome. Relationships between myriads of parameters, characteristic of parameters - are difficult to define. Once the parameters are discovered, you&#39;re confronted with the next challenge: sanitize the data before processing it. Subject matter experts must statistically analyze relationships between parameters to weed out noise and outliers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Next comes the major challenge: how to derive a statistical model from the parameters for predictive analytics? Traditional solutions rely mostly on linear regression models. But rarely does your business world fit into simplistic linear models.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>What if an intelligent machine could automatically:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul class="int-content">\r\n	<li>identify parameters (predictors) which impact a business outcome, and</li>\r\n	<li>generate reasonably accurate statistical model for predictive analytics so that you trust its results? It would help jump start and accelerate the results, freeing up your data scientists to refine the generated model.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Veracity in your big data solution would give you the confidence in using its results to run your business better - based on objective, quantitative information. That&#39;s the promise of the Intelligent Analytical Modeler.</p>\r\n', NULL, NULL, 1, '2014-01-15 04:38:04', '2014-01-23 07:33:37'),
(8, 'Enterprise Quality Solutions', 3, 'Enterprise Quality Solutions', '1389778756_1389778756.jpg', NULL, NULL, 'enterprise-quality-solutions', 'pagetemplates/default_template', 1, NULL, '', '', '<h3>Call Quality Manager</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Datanomer&rsquo;s Big Data Solutions are comprehensive and unique: based on expert systems autonomics and cognitive science, intuitive, accurate and can easily automate complex processes. One such solution is Call Quality Solution for enterprise and carriers. Some of the biggest enterprise in the world have benefited financially from this solution. CQM is our flagship Big Data Solution.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Voice Quality Manager</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Datanomers&rsquo; VQA is a big data analytical solution that detects and remediates voice quality in near real time. The solution reduces customer churn and helps you bring in high margin premium traffic for enterprise customers, mobile operators, service providers and wholesale carriers.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>IPX QoS Performance Manager</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The promise of IPX technology is to provide richer and higher quality of user experience for the end subscriber. However, keeping the promise is extremely challenging unless rigorous quality management measures are put in place. The measures must comprehensively address the 3 levels of QoS for IPX deployments &ndash; Transport, IPX Service and User Experience.</p>\r\n', '', NULL, NULL, 1, '2014-01-15 04:39:16', '2014-01-16 06:56:33'),
(9, 'Fraud Management', 3, 'Fraud Management', '1389779898_1389779898.jpg', NULL, NULL, 'fraud-management', 'pagetemplates/default_template', 1, NULL, '', '', '<h3>False Answer Supervision</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The carrier business is competitive: voice products are increasingly commoditized, and margins are getting razor thin. Carriers need to differentiate from their competitors, by providing better, cost-effective, service to high value customers. That&rsquo;s what Datanomer&rsquo;s solutions help you deliver. Datanomers Big Data Solutions are comprehensive and unique: based on expert systems autonomics and cognitive science, are intuitive, accurate and can easily automate complex processes. One such solution is False Answer Supervision. The biggest telecom carriers in the world have benefited financially from the solutions.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>International Revenue Share Fraud</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>International Revenue Share Fraud (IRSF) is one of the most menacing frauds plaguing the telecom industry. IRSF is caused by the artificial inflation of traffic or traffic pumping to the premium rate numbers in the world.<br />\r\nDatanomers&rsquo; International Revenue Share Fraud tool is a big data analytical solution that detects International Revenue Share Fraud (IRSF) and remediates it in near real time which will avert huge financial losses for enterprise customers, mobile operators, service providers and wholesale carriers.</p>\r\n', '<div class="solutions">\r\n<h3 class="heading-main">Big Data Solution: False Answer Supervision</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The carrier business is competitive: voice products are increasingly commoditized, and margins are getting razor thin. Carriers need to differentiate from their competitors, by providing better, cost-effective, service to high value customers. That&rsquo;s what Datanomer&rsquo;s solutions help you deliver. Datanomers Big Data Solutions are comprehensive and unique: based on expert systems autonomics and cognitive science, are intuitive, accurate and can easily automate complex processes. One such solution is False Answer Supervision. The biggest telecom carriers in the world have benefited financially from the solutions.<br />\r\nOnce you deploy our Fraud Management Solution, you will notice an immediate improvement in route quality. How?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Because, our advanced statistical machine-learning state-of-the-art technology is highly accurate and has global coverage that enables the deployment of our solution to break even in under a year. Your route quality improves substantially as you rid it of fraud. Your customers notice and give you more business, especially for premium traffic with higher margins. Your business differentiates and grows.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>The Challenge</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>What is Fraud and How Does it Afflict Carriers?</strong><br />\r\nFraud has permeated in both carriers and enterprises, bleeding over $6B dollars annually from carriers. The result: Unhappy Customers Switching Carriers, Lost revenue for Carriers because of no fault of their own, Customer churn. Enterprises get unexpected, large bills and demands for payment.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Fraud Types</strong><br />\r\nThere are several types of fraud, But most important ones are:<br />\r\n1- False Answer Supervision (FAS),<br />\r\n2- Premium Rate Fraud (IPRF) and<br />\r\n3- Mobile Fraud.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class="left-side"><img alt="" src="img/img-9.png" /></div>\r\n\r\n<p>FAS is perhaps the most prevalent and is under the control of international carriers. So What is FAS? FAS occurs when a call is falsely answered by a downstream carrier so they can start billing well in advance of the real answer. Even worse for customers is a phenomenon, known as call hijacking, where the call is routed to an automated voice system designed to keep them on the phone while billing continues; not only do they get a huge bill, but the call does not even reach the dialed customer.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>IPRF occurs when a premium rate service provider colludes with a hacker to break into a PBX, launch a large number of calls to an international premium rate destination, get a share of the profits from the distant service provider, and disappear before the break-in is found. The enterprise whose PBX was hacked refuses to pay the bill and carriers in the chain dispute billing, resulting in large losses for all concerned!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mobile Fraud is very damaging to the mobile industry with cloned SIMs and roaming fraud generating many unpaid calls to distant high rate premium codes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="width:100%; float:left;"><strong>Carriers Fight Back</strong><br />\r\nCarriers are now increasingly serious about fighting fraud. They have banded together, under the aegis of the standards i3Forum, to publish a process that removes traffic for weeks from those carriers without efficient fraud management systems, resulting in considerable revenue loss.<br />\r\nIf you don&#39;t police fraud in your network, you risk losing revenue.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="width:100%; float:left;">There are probe based solutions in the market that do not come close to our solution in delivering features and functions and aren&#39;t effective in eradicating FAS. They have their limitations:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul class="int-content">\r\n	<li>In case of probe based solution, you need to have the carrier launch several synthetic calls to a all these destinations. If not FAS goes undetected.</li>\r\n	<li>Fraudsters are getting smart: for example, blended FAS which is done intelligently by the fraudulent suppliers in the network to avoid detection: FAS is switched on and off. for probe&#39;s synthetic calls to detect such blended FAS, the carrier needs to place several test calls to the same destination, daily, and then out of several to a destination, a couple may detect blended FAS. when you have blended FAS happening in the intl destinations, the OPex rises, the solution becomes more expensive than the issue it addresses.</li>\r\n	<li>Probe based solutions cannot handle the volume of CDRs our solution can handle</li>\r\n	<li>Probe based solution cannot accurately quantify fraud. Datanomers&rsquo; statistical solution is not academic. It quantifies fraud. It helps you make decisions to remediate supplier and goes a step further than all other solutions in the market. Our FAS solution stores the cdrs of fraud calls which provides you with the irrefutable evidence that a supplier was doing FAS. Now we can dispute billing w/ suppliers, negotiate better rates with them, trouble shoot the issue, and insist on better quality</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class="left-side"><img alt="" src="img/img-10.png" /></div>\r\n\r\n<h3 style="width:100%; float:left;">The Solution</h3>\r\n\r\n<p style="width:100%; float:left;"><strong>Datanomer&rsquo;s Unique Solution</strong><br />\r\nDatanomer&rsquo;s fraud management solutions are the most technologically advanced on the market and some of the largest Global Carriers rely on Datanomer&rsquo;s solution to combat FAS, They statistically identify fraud directly from a carrier&rsquo;s CDRs. These global carriers have expressed <u>tremendous faith in our solutions</u>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="width:100%; float:left;"><strong>Datanomers FAS Solution Differentiator: </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul class="int-content">\r\n	<li>Accuracy of 95% while detecting 90% of the fraud.</li>\r\n	<li>64-Bit industrial server architecture scales to 200M CDRs daily with peak processing rate of 10M CDRs per hour.</li>\r\n	<li>Detects fraud in near real-time. It can easily integrate into your operations systems to stop fraud quickly before it is noticed, reducing customer trouble ticket volume by 15%.</li>\r\n	<li>Stores fraud CDRs so that you can quantify the extent of the fraud, create reports on various suppliers and destinations, and withhold fraudulent payments.</li>\r\n	<li>Covers 100% of worldwide destinations with no extra costs of test calls and probes</li>\r\n	<li>With Datanomers&rsquo; statistical solution, you do not have opex. because it doesn&#39;t generate synthetic calls</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class="left-side"><img alt="" src="http://datanomers.checkyourprojects.com/app/webroot/ck_files/images/img-9.png" /></div>\r\n\r\n<p class="int-content">Datanomers FAS solution is deployed in your data center managed and administered by you, or as some carriers prefer, in our private cloud and managed and administered by us. Our solution breaks even in under a year, the financials that prove this have been vetted by standards forum and independently verified by carriers</p>\r\n\r\n<div class="left-side"><img alt="" src="http://datanomers.checkyourprojects.com/app/webroot/ck_files/images/img-10.png" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div class="left-side"><img alt="" src="http://datanomers.checkyourprojects.com/app/webroot/ck_files/images/img-11.png" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="solutions">\r\n<h3 class="heading-main">Big Data Solution: International Revenue Share Fraud IRSF&trade;</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3>Overview</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>International Revenue Share Fraud (IRSF) is one of the most menacing frauds plaguing the telecom industry. IRSF is caused by the artificial inflation of traffic or traffic pumping to the premium rate numbers in the world.<br />\r\nDatanomers&rsquo; International Revenue Share Fraud tool is a big data analytical solution that detects International Revenue Share Fraud (IRSF) and remediates it in near real time which will avert huge financial losses for enterprise customers, mobile operators, service providers and wholesale carriers.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>The Challenge</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>According to the Communications Fraud Control Association (CFCA), telecom industry lost close to <u>$4B billion</u> to revenue share fraud.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Typically IRSF involves a nexus between the following. </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>PRN (Premium Rate Number) Aggregators: who obtain range of fraudulent premium rate numbers (PRN) countries like Lithuania, Sao Tome and enter into an agreement with service providers falsely claiming entertainment services.</li>\r\n	<li>Hackers or the fraudsters who generate traffic. They either hack a PBX of a company, or clone SIM cards and generate millions of artificial calls to premium numbers.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Hackers and the revenue share providers share the revenue generated by the fraudulent calls which will be billed either to the end customer or some carrier in the routing flow.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class="left-side"><img alt="" src="http://datanomers.checkyourprojects.com/app/webroot/ck_files/images/img-12.png" /></div>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The alarming fact about IRSF is that it is triggered by many other means of fraud like PBX hacking, SIM card cloning, International roaming fraud, subscription theft.</li>\r\n	<li>These premium rate services are the eternal cash cow for the telecom carriers and they are more than willing to buy premium rate services without sufficient checks and balances to distinguish between a rigged and a genuine player.</li>\r\n	<li>The delays in identification of the nature and volume of the calls, delays in blocking the numbers makes IRSF extremely difficult to detect and combat.</li>\r\n	<li>The final straw is the nature of the carrier model, the money transfer has already been done to fraudulent providers who cannot be traced after the fraud has been discovered.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>The Solution</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Datanomers has come up with the state of the art big data analytical solution that detects and remediates IRSF in near real time. Below are</p>\r\n\r\n<table align="left" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td class="brown-bg">Features</td>\r\n			<td class="brown-bg">Datanomers Solution</td>\r\n			<td class="brown-bg">Competitor Solutions</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td class="brown-bg">Accuracy</td>\r\n			<td class="grey-bg" valign="top">\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li>95% Accuracy</li>\r\n				<li>Patented Algorithms</li>\r\n				<li>Advanced Statistics like <u>Central Limit Theorem, entropy of random variables</u></li>\r\n				<li>Industry Expertise</li>\r\n			</ul>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td class="grey-bg" valign="top">\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li>Rely heavily on industry expertise and hot lists of premium service ranges</li>\r\n				<li>Elementary Statistics</li>\r\n				<li>Pre-defined patterns which generates a slew of False positives</li>\r\n			</ul>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td class="brown-bg">Coverage</td>\r\n			<td valign="top">\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li>Low Grade IRSF and Blended IRSF are caught in near real time.</li>\r\n				<li>Advanced Machine Learning working off the 200-300 million CDRs</li>\r\n				<li>Algorithms based on Covariance , K-Mean clustering of random variables</li>\r\n				<li>Low-Grade IRSF, Blended IRSF is caught and alerted</li>\r\n			</ul>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td valign="top">\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li>Pre-defined pattern to detect</li>\r\n				<li>Missed True positives</li>\r\n			</ul>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td class="brown-bg">Remediation</td>\r\n			<td class="grey-bg" valign="top">\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li>Auto-Removal/blockage of fraudulent ranges in near real time</li>\r\n				<li>ACTIONABLE INTELLIGENCE</li>\r\n			</ul>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td class="grey-bg" valign="top">\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li>Delays in detection and remediation</li>\r\n			</ul>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td class="brown-bg">Evidence</td>\r\n			<td valign="top">\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li>CDR(Call Detail Record) Repository stores fraudulent CDRs as irrefutable evidence</li>\r\n			</ul>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td valign="top">\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li>No CDR evidence for missed true positives and wrong CDRs for false</li>\r\n			</ul>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td class="brown-bg">Scalability</td>\r\n			<td class="grey-bg" valign="top">\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li>Scalable solution based on big data analytics</li>\r\n			</ul>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td class="grey-bg" valign="top">\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li>Questionable scalability</li>\r\n			</ul>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td class="brown-bg">Process Improvement</td>\r\n			<td valign="top">\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li>Email/SNMP notification</li>\r\n				<li>Better Operations KPI</li>\r\n				<li>Better SLAs</li>\r\n			</ul>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td valign="top">\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li>Operations team work with a myriad of tools and troubleshooting is slow and tedious</li>\r\n			</ul>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td class="brown-bg">IRSF Dashboard</td>\r\n			<td class="grey-bg" valign="top">\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li>Customers get a peek on how well fraud is kept under check</li>\r\n				<li>Rich set of reporting</li>\r\n			</ul>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td class="grey-bg" valign="top">\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li>Basic Reports</li>\r\n			</ul>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>In a nutshell Datanomers&rsquo; IRSF solution helps you to Grow business strategically with a quality message. Big deals on the anvil rely on this. Quality is going to be the key in the years to come and Datanomers will help you be the game changer.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n', NULL, NULL, 1, '2014-01-15 04:58:18', '2014-01-16 06:57:07'),
(10, 'Sales Intelligence Tool', 3, 'Sales Intelligence Tool', '1389779997_1389779997.jpg', NULL, NULL, 'sales-intelligence-tool', 'pagetemplates/default_template', 0, NULL, '', '', '<p>Every Industry vertical strives for the ultimate goal of increasing sales and revenues. In the telecom industry that works on tight margins and stiffer competition, the need is even more profound.<br />\r\nDatanomers Big Data Sales Intelligence Solution intelligently identifies sales opportunities and boosts revenues- for wholesale carriers and mobile operators. The solution which is based on machine learning and advanced statistics analyzes processes huge volumes of CDRs which are of the magnitude of 200-300 million CDRs daily.</p>\r\n', '<h3>Overview</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Every Industry vertical strives for the ultimate goal of increasing sales and revenues. In the telecom industry that works on tight margins and stiffer competition, the need is even more profound.<br />\r\nDatanomers Big Data Sales Intelligence Solution intelligently identifies sales opportunities and boosts revenues- for wholesale carriers and mobile operators. The solution which is based on machine learning and advanced statistics analyzes processes huge volumes of CDRs which are of the magnitude of 200-300 million CDRs daily.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Identifies unexplored markets or destinations for your existing customers that you do not currently receive traffic to so that you can focus your marketing campaigns on those markets to these customers.</li>\r\n	<li>Identifies your potential customers by determining the origination of where you get the traffic so that you target better rates and pricing to these potential customers.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>The Challenge</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>If you are a wholesale carrier, How do you explore new markets with your existing customers?</li>\r\n	<li>If you are a mobile operator, How do you decrease the subscriber revenue leakage to the OTT applications? How do you decrease the subscriber churn?</li>\r\n	<li>How do you find new potential customers?</li>\r\n	<li>How do you focus your marketing campaigns on the right markets?</li>\r\n	<li>How do you customize your products and offers to the right customers in the right destinations or markets?</li>\r\n	<li>How do you enhance Customer experience?</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>The Solution</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Datanomers Big Data Sales Intelligence Solution works off your CDRs to identify significant current and missing markets or destinations for your current and potential customers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The kernel of Sales Intelligence tool has 2 solutions running in parallel.<br />\r\n1) The Gatherer<br />\r\n2) The Hunter</p>\r\n\r\n<p><u>The Gatherer solution</u> looks at your existing customers and finds opportunities to grow business and increase revenues. The self-learning solution identifies for the existing customer</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Where their community of interest lies.</li>\r\n	<li>What specific market breakouts are attractive.</li>\r\n	<li>What markets or regions are other competing customers looking at, that needs to be addressed by this customer.</li>\r\n	<li>Presents a comprehensive dashboard on missing traffic including potential size, volume and performance of other customers.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class="left-side"><img alt="" src="http://datanomers.checkyourprojects.com/app/webroot/ck_files/images/img-7.png" /></div>\r\n\r\n<p><u>The Hunter solution</u> automatically looks for new customers that could be signed up</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The advanced Big data solution finds out potential customers that uses the service and can directly terminate through you for the same quality and better rates.</li>\r\n	<li>It identifies origination networks where the potential carriers can build direct relationship to win business and offer better quality with higher margins, and fine-grained code to destination mapping (to pin-point origination networks).</li>\r\n	<li>For the potential customers our solution identifies the potential regions, volumes to make an attractive business case.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class="left-side"><img alt="" src="http://datanomers.checkyourprojects.com/app/webroot/ck_files/images/img-8.png" /></div>\r\n\r\n<p>The solution resides in your data center (License model), or as some carriers prefer, in Datanomers cloud (SaaS model).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Sales Intelligence tool helps win more revenues &ndash; sales. It easily integrates in your sales process. It helps you identify, strategize, plan for and execute your sales opportunity by presenting compelling business logic for your customers. It makes your sales opportunity management process and methodology complete. It will help you make a BIG Impact in your company.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Contact us at <a href="mailto:leads@datanomers.com"><u>leads@datanomers.com</u></a> for an initial evaluation.</p>\r\n', NULL, NULL, 1, '2014-01-15 04:59:57', '2014-01-16 06:57:49'),
(11, 'Unstructured Intelligence Tools', 3, 'Unstructured Intelligence Tools', '1389780072_1389780072.jpg', NULL, NULL, 'unstructured-intelligence-tools', 'pagetemplates/default_template', 0, NULL, '', '', '<p>The Unstructured Intelligence Tools from Datanomer help mine cognitive insights from your unstructured data. The unstructured intelligence toolset is built on statistical machine learning and on natural language processing (NLP). The tools help eliminate the noise and organizes valuable information in structured form for logical deductions and inferences based on the business context.</p>\r\n', '<p>The Unstructured Intelligence Tools from Datanomers helps mine cognitive insights from your unstructured data. The unstructured intelligence toolset is built on statistical machine learning and on natural language processing (NLP). The tools helps eliminate the noise and organizes valuable information in structured form for logical deductions and inferences based on the business context.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Unstrctured data happens to be the largest untapped resource of information in most organizations. IDC reports this data resource to grow as large as 90% of all your organization&#39;s data in this decade. There is a wealth of information important to business burried under the unstructured data. However, it is extremely challenging to mine the information - thus for many it remains &quot;untapped&quot;. The mining exercise is perceived to be expensive, time consuming and without guarantees for discovery of gems. Not anymore, Datanomers&rsquo; Unstructured Intelligence Toolset allows you to mine the intelligence systematically and quantifiably step by step.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Unstructured Intelligence Miner toolset allows you to converge rapidly to cognitive insights - the hardest challenges out there - speed and cognition. Unstructured data is rich in insights but at the same time is extremely rich in the noise as well. The sooner you eliminate the noise, the faster you would get to the gems. The noise here being all data that is irrelevant to pursuance of the analytics goal. That&#39;s the promise from Datanomers UIM SieveSet to eliminate all noise from the original unstructured data and leave you with rich contents ready for next level of analytics. The Datanomers UIM InsightSet allows you to mine actionable intelligence from the noise-free rich contents using tools based on advanced machine learning.</p>\r\n', NULL, NULL, 1, '2014-01-15 05:01:12', '2014-01-17 01:01:11'),
(12, 'Call Quality Manager', 8, 'Call Quality Manager', '1389780761_1389780761.jpg', NULL, NULL, 'call-quality-manager', 'pagetemplates/default_template', 0, NULL, '', '', NULL, '<div class="solutions">\r\n<div class="left-side"><img alt="" src="http://datanomers.checkyourprojects.com/app/webroot/ck_files/images/img-1.jpg"  /></div>\r\n\r\n<p>Datanomers&rsquo; Big Data Solutions are comprehensive and unique: based on expert systems autonomics and cognitive science, intuitive, accurate and can easily automate complex processes. One such solution is Call Quality Solution for enterprise and carriers. Some of the biggest enterprises in the world have benefited financially from this solution. CQM is our flagship Big Data Solution.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>The Challenge</h3>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-bottom:24px;">Call Quality has been defined and measured very narrowly in the industry. It&rsquo;s synonymous with &ldquo;voice quality,&rdquo; usually measured by ITU-T G.107 and P.862 that map to Mean Opinion Score (MOS). A call, however, has many other facets than voice. For instance, a subscriber is on a mobile, driving along, the call may have sounded fine while driving, but it dropped, and that&rsquo;s a big nuisance. The subscriber will have to redial to resume conversation, worse still if it were an enterprise subscriber on a conference call who has to enter several digits to log back in.<br />\r\nAnother scenario: a subscriber repeatedly dials an international termination, only to find that the call goes into a black hole (either due to excessive post dial delay or poor completion rate). It&rsquo;s irritating.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Do any of the following scenarios sound familiar?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Do your calls go into a black hole? (retry several times, before your calls connect)</li>\r\n	<li>Do your calls have excessive post dial delay (wait for ringback, hangup, redial and wait longer for ringback)</li>\r\n	<li>Do your calls disrupt midway? (mobile calls drop, VoIP calls disconnect after a couple of seconds)</li>\r\n	<li>Do your calls have poor audio? (considerable echo, choppy or robotic audio, bursts of one-way voice)</li>\r\n	<li>Does your management solution pin-point root cause and how to fix it?</li>\r\n	<li>Do you get bills for incorrect amount? (routed to spurious announcements and billed, hacked PBX originates premium rate international calls)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>If you answer yes to any or all of the above scenarios, your Quality of User Experience (QUES) is not ideal and Datanomers Big Data CQM Solution will help.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>The Solution</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Our Call Quality Solution ensures better Quality of User Experience. What do we mean by QUES (Quality of User Experience)? Calls are monitored proactively in real time and re-routed to a better carrier to avoid bad user experience. Such calls are assigned a very low, subpar QUES Score by our Solution and our CQM Manager not only flags these calls but also suggest how to re-route such calls for high QUES score and low customer churn which Results in high customer satisfaction. To ensure high QUE, the alerts are generated in near real-time using Advanced Statistical Algorithms and Automation, You re-route the traffic to an alternative carrier that is better and recommended by &quot;Our Intelligent Analytics Modeler (IAM)&quot;, One of its kind in the market. This proactive management differentiates a voice service offered by a carrier or enterprise. Our Call Quality Manager works off your CDRs and differentiates from its competitors in that it is the first Solution in the market that provides Comprehensive State-of-the-Art QUES Score by managing the entire calling experience for an end user (call drops, high post dial delay, poor audio, poor connection rate - comprehensive QUES score). Most Industry Solutions today just monitor audio Quality (MOS)<br />\r\nOur solution has the ability to monitor 100 to 150 million calls per 24 hours in real time and is Comprehensive and based on Advanced Statistical Machine Learning Algorithms that monitors end to end User Experience to ensure Excellent QUES Score for a converged (fixed &amp; mobile) ubiquitous anytime-anywhere communication for the carriers and enterprise</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Datanomers Call Quality kernel &ndash; Call Setup Quality(CSQ) </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Solves ECR (Excessive Call Retries)</li>\r\n	<li>Solves HPDD(High Post Dial Delay)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class="left-side"><img alt="" src="img/img-2.png" /></div>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Datanomers Call Quality kernel &ndash; Call Conversational Quality(CCQ)</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul class="int-content">\r\n	<li>Solves ECD (Excessive Call Disruptions)</li>\r\n	<li>Solves PAQ(Poor Audio Quality)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class="left-side"><img alt="" src="img/img-3.png" /></div>\r\n\r\n<h3>Why Must You Implement Call Quality Manager Now?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Much of the world whether for enterprise or consumer traffic is still tied to uni-dimensional (call duration, completion rate) or MOS, which measure voice. The early birds, some of whom have moved towards comprehensive QUES, will have first movers advantage. VoIPX is on the horizon, offering superior MPLS transport to the feature-rich IMS platform. It&rsquo;s big promise is to enhance the quality of call experience for subscribers. With considerable investment in VoIPX, it makes a lot of sense for carriers and enterprises to measure and manage the performance of their VoIPX network for quality. Many customers, enterprises, OTTs, and mobile providers &ndash; are particularly concerned about subscriber&rsquo;s experience of a call. It directly impacts subscriber churn. They have, or are implementing, Call Quality Manager. Those enterprises who also do, stand to gain their business.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>What Differentiates Datanomers Solution from Others?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Datanomers&rsquo; Call Quality Manager works off your network Call Detail Records to detect poor call quality in near real-time by statistically analyzing CDRs to identify the small variations in call patterns that represent poor calls. Multiple statistical models, each representing a use case, operate in parallel. It resides in your data center (License model), or as some customers prefer, in our Partner&rsquo;s cloud (SaaS model). This results in several advantages that are unmatched:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class="full-width-img"><img alt="" src="img/img-4.png" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div class="full-width-img"><img alt="" src="img/img-5.png" /></div>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-top:10px;">Try our solution free for 15 days.</p>\r\n\r\n<div style="float:left;">\r\n<h3>Our Differentiator: A Next-Gen Approach &ndash; High ROI</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Manage for better user experience. End-to-end to increase revenue</li>\r\n	<li>Get rid of poor quality &ndash; bad calls, fraudulent billing &ndash; for sensitive customers - Differentiate from competition</li>\r\n	<li>High accuracy. No false positives. True positives alerted in near real-time, resolve issue before impact. Lower operational expense</li>\r\n	<li>Actionable intelligence into how to resolve the issue &ndash; identifies better suppliers in your route</li>\r\n	<li>Integrate to automate operations process. Works off CDRs. No massive probes and agents deployments. Simpler. Low capex, opex</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>We Help Run Your Business Better. How? Let&rsquo;s explain:</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The carrier business is competitive: voice products are increasingly commoditized, margins razor thin. Now more than ever, carriers need to differentiate from their respective competitors, by providing better, cost-effective, service to high value customers. That&rsquo;s what Datanomers solutions help you deliver. Once you deploy our Call Quality Management Solution, you&rsquo;ll notice an immediate improvement in route quality. How? Because our advanced statistical machine-learning state-of-the-art technology is highly accurate and has global coverage: All at very reasonable price that enables the deployment to break even in under a year. Your route quality improves substantially as you rid it of poor calls. Your customers notice and give you more business, especially for premium traffic with higher margins. Your business differentiates and grows.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Solution Deployed at Carriers and Enterprises</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Tier 1 carriers, MSPs have already benefitted from Datanomers Call Quality Management solution. It offers a novel approach for wholesale and retail to manage mobile telephony for better user experience, low expense, high ROI, and easily scales for the largest deployment. Additionally, the side benefits of Low capex, opex enable our customers to utilize our market-proven solution with minimal impact.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--end solutions-->', NULL, NULL, 1, '2014-01-15 05:12:41', '2014-01-16 04:16:57');
